  abstract  = {This work introduces a novel methodological framework for analyzing health trajectories and survival outcomes in heart failure patients. We combine NLP techniques for characterizing patient trajectories, unsupervised clustering with a new metric for measuring diagnosis distances, and survival analysis to assess patient outcomes.},
